  "label": "Cinder Cantina Loftroom",
  "description": "Cinder Cantina Loftroom serves as a cramped sleeping chamber partitioned from the tavern’s slagcrete vault by riveted plasteel framing and soot-darkened insulation. A narrow cot and a bolted locker sit beneath low conduit runs, their surfaces perpetually filmed with fine ash tracked in from Ashenward City’s vitrified streets. Bruised violet light-strips leak through a louvered vent, casting hard reflections across basalt blocks and worn stone flags. Shielded vox-baffles and a heavy intake grille maintain a sealed, pressurized stillness that reduces the city’s ash-gales to a distant metallic hush.",
